1. Ja *smislim* da treba da idemo na odmor. (I come up with the idea that we should go on vacation.)
2. On je *smislio* inovativan način da poboljša prodaju. (He came up with an innovative way to improve sales.)
3. Kada sam *smislila* šta želim da kažem, bilo je prekasno. (When I came up with what I wanted to say, it was too late.)
4. Ti nikada ne bi mogao *smisliti* tako dobru šalu kao ja. (You could never come up with a joke as good as me.)
5. Oni su *smislili* način da uštede novac. (They came up with a way to save money.)
6. Da li ste *smislili* plan za vikend? (Have you come up with a plan for the weekend?)
7. Mama je *smislila* sjajan recept za ručak. (Mom came up with a great recipe for lunch.)
8. Deca su *smislila* igru koja je jako zabavna. (The kids came up with a game that is very fun.)
9. Kada sam *smislila* ovaj projekat, nisam znala koliko će biti uspešan. (When I came up with this project, I didn't know how successful it would be.)
10. Nije lako *smisliti* originalan poklon za rođendan. (It's not easy to come up with an original birthday gift.)